": 1006}, {\"ngram\": \"the dimensions\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1024}, {\"ngram\": \"the finished product\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a bit more patient, more steady and more aware of small details.\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1119, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"small details\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1118}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So that helped me a lot.\\\"\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1145, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After winning the gold medal in 2023, Ms Wong is now representing Singapore on the global stage in WorldSkills 2024, the \\\"Olympics of vocational skills\\\", which is being held in Lyon, France, from Sept 10 to 15.\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1357, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1213, \"end\": 1222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.9999999957128693, \"rank\": 4.197256225703656e-09, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}, {\"begin\": 1324, \"end\": 1328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\", \"score\": 0.9986578596022586, \"rank\": 0.0013435594015958588, \"text\": \"Lyon\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\"}, {\"begin\": 1330, \"end\": 1336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9956074639055847, \"rank\": 0.0035669525697636533, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"Ms Wong\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1192}, {\"ngram\": \"the global stage\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"WorldSkills\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1257}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"Olympics\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1277}, {\"ngram\": \"vocational skills\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1298}, {\"ngram\": \"Sept\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She told The Straits Times that she was not surprised to discover that she was the only female out of 26 competitors there as well.\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1368, \"end\": 1385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Straits_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Straits Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Straits_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Straits_Times\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only female\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1453}, {\"ngram\": \"26 competitors\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1475}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am here, and I beat all the guys in Singapore.\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1531, \"end\": 1540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.9999999957128693, \"rank\": 4.197256225703656e-09, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the guys\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel like I am able to show a different side of feminine power, where I can do it as well as the guys.\\\"\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a different side\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1590}, {\"ngram\": \"feminine power\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1608}, {\"ngram\": \"the guys\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her training for the competitions started in March 2022, when she had just started her second year of study at Singapore Polytechnic (SP), pursuing a diploma in aeronautical engineering.\", \"from\": 1651, \"to\": 1837, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1762, \"end\": 1783,